<HEADLINE>
DISNEY PULLS TAPE FOR SUBLIMINAL SMUT
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE McNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
