already brought several angry critiques from historians and
commentators over how it interprets the Cold War and how it assigns
blame. The Times asked three historians with different perspectives
to assess the series. The stories were TV-COLDWAR-RADOSH,
TV-COLDWAR-GARDNER, TV-COLDWAR-GADDIS.
