<P>
   BKN-LABOR (Undated) _ An in-depth look at how relations between
the NBA's players and owners had deteriorated over the six months
of the owners' lockout, a standoff that ended only last Wednesday
with an 11th-hour deal that narrowly averted the first cancellation
of an entire professional sports season. By Mike Wise with Selena
Roberts.
</P>
<P>
   2-column hed.
