<HEADLINE>
COMMENTARY: YALE GENE POOL SEEN AS ROUTE TO BETTER BABY
</HEADLINE>
 (bl) 
By JOSEPH BERGER   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
