   IMPEACH-WELLSTONE _WASHINGTON _ Sen. Paul Wellstone, D-Minn.,
says he is ``skeptical'' that the impeachment charges against
President Clinton warrant his removal from office. His comment is
one of the strongest indications of a probable vote since the
senators swore Thursday to ``do impartial justice.'' (Malone, Cox
News Service) 10. MOVED
</P>
